// fox — Strix Halo desktop, Apple Studio Display over USB4.
//
// The Studio Display's phantom secondary DP stream and its DPMS-wake quirk are
// handled at runtime by home/studio-display.nix — resolved by make/model,
// because the DP connector numbers drift across reboots. A static
// `output "DP-N" { off }` block used to live here but went stale the moment
// the connectors renumbered (DP-5/6 → DP-7/8), re-arming the phantom.
